1148	The narrative above is realised on the Lean side by the named substrate lemmas
1149	collected here. They feed the Stacks-00OE Krull-dimension formula
1150	\cref{lem:smooth_algebra_krull_dim_formula} and the regular-stalk assembly,
1151	either directly or through the Jacobian regular-sequence witness.
